@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "User Interface" as UserInterface
participant "Image Processing" as ImageProcessing
participant "Voice Cloning" as VoiceCloning
participant "Avatar Customization" as AvatarCustomization
participant "Natural Language Processing (NLP)" as NaturalLanguageProcessingNLP
participant "Authentication and Authorization" as AuthenticationandAuthorization
participant "Avatar Creation" as AvatarCreation
participant "Emotion Expression" as EmotionExpression
participant "System Administration" as SystemAdministration
UserInterface ->> ImageProcessing : Upload Image
ImageProcessing -> AvatarCustomization : Process Image
VoiceCloning -> AvatarCustomization : Clone Voice
AvatarCustomization ->> EmotionExpression : Update Emotion
NaturalLanguageProcessingNLP -> AvatarCustomization : Process Conversation
AvatarCreation -> AvatarCustomization : Create Avatar
AuthenticationandAuthorization -> AvatarCreation : Authenticate User
SystemAdministration -> AuthenticationandAuthorization : Create Admin Account
UserInterface ->> VoiceCloning : Record Voice
UserInterface ->> NaturalLanguageProcessingNLP : Converse with Avatar
UserInterface ->> AvatarCustomization : Customize Avatar
AvatarCustomization -> AvatarCreation : Update Avatar
AvatarCreation -> AvatarCustomization : Create Avatar
@enduml